</p>
<p>So add <code>$stripeSubscription = </code> in front of that line. Then, add
<code>$this-&gt;get('subscription_helper')-&gt;addSubscriptionToUser()</code> passing it <code>$stripeSubscription</code>
and the currently-logged-in <code>$user</code>:</p>
