</p>
<p>Phew! That may have seemed like a lot, but ultimately, this line just makes sure
that there is a subscription row in our table that's associated with this user
and up-to-date with the subscription and plan IDs. </p>
<p>Let's go try it out. Add a new subscription to your cart, fill out the fake
credit card information and hit checkout. No errors! To the account page! Yes!
The subscription is active! Our database is up-to-date.</p>

    
